cat command:
cat homework             1st  crat file    2nd time read file
cat >hello               creat with text
cat >>hello              add new line old file
cat hello > hello2        old file copy new file
cat hello hello2 > combo    combination creat new file
cat -n hello   or cat -b hello               show file line number
cat -e hello             show $ in end every line
cat > hello3 << EOF      everyline star pont <
cat *                    show all file content
cat weeks.txt | tac | cat | cat | tac
eco this is  test file > test    creat test file with curson mark
cat /etc/passwd | more
cat /etc/passwd | less

